QuestData.Title: Work Order: The Klaxxi I
QuestData.Description: <Though Yoon's writing leaves something to be desired, it's nice to still have a little piece of him on the farm.>$b$bAn order came in this morning from the Klaxxi. Strangely enough they are requesting mogu pumpkins for some kind of research.$b$bI find it's best not to ask them too many questions...$b$bBest get started on their order. I'd hate to see what a bug of that size could do to your crops if you don't!
QuestData.LogDescription: Plant 8 Mogu Pumpkin Seeds on Sunsong Ranch.
